ate sharing service for pet knowledge","status":"completed","activeForm":"Creating sharing service"},{"content":"Integrate memory system with chat","status":"in_progress","activeForm":"Integrating memory with chat"},{"content":"Phase 2: Check and verify the implementation","status":"pending","activeForm":"Checking and verifying implementation"},{"content":"Phase 3: Finish the task","status":"pending","activeForm":"Finishing the task"},{"content":"Phase 4: Create pull request","status":"pending","activeForm":"Creating pull request"}],"verificationNudgeNeeded":false}}
